```markdown
# Lean Session — YYYY-MM-DD (Session N)

**Goal**: <what theorem, lemma, or formalization task was the target>
**Source**: <informal statement or paper reference, if any>
**Outcome**: <filled at session end: Proved / Partial / Stuck / Abandoned>

---

